Author:

    josejp2424 <puppylinuxjosejp2424@gmail.com>

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. License texts
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Full license texts are included in the LICENSES directory:

    LICENSES/MPL-2.0
    LICENSES/MIT
    LICENSES/GPL-3.0-or-later

If this repository keeps the upstream picom LICENSES directory, the original
upstream license files must be preserved.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. Summary
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The license structure of this repository is:

    Original picom source code:
        MPL-2.0 AND MIT

    New picom-compatible source files:
        MPL-2.0, unless otherwise stated

    EssoraFM-specific integration files:
        GPL-3.0-or-later, unless otherwise stated

This means that EssoraFM Picom is not licensed as a single-license project.
It is a fork with preserved upstream licensing and additional EssoraFM-specific
files under GPL-3.0-or-later.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
5. SPDX recommendations
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For original or inherited picom source files, keep the existing SPDX header:

    SPDX-License-Identifier: MPL-2.0 AND MIT

For new picom-compatible source files, use:

    SPDX-License-Identifier: MPL-2.0

For EssoraFM-specific scripts, packaging files and integration files, use:

    SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later

Example header for EssoraFM-specific shell scripts:

    # SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later
    # Copyright (C) 2026 josejp2424
    # Author: josejp2424 <puppylinuxjosejp2424@gmail.com>

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6. Disclaimer
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This license notice is intended to clarify the licensing structure of the
EssoraFM Picom fork. It does not remove or replace any upstream license,
copyright notice or contributor attribution from the original picom project.
